{"tid":691191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡推3款「特金會」紀念幣　售價211至8000港元","createTime":"2018-06-05T13:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T14:02:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"717dd47dd71ec846f21f5601e3be2b61d734dbae","tid":691191,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T13:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180605/s00005/19001e8caf90055bf15ee1361c993ead.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180605%2Fs00005%2F19001e8caf90055bf15ee1361c993ead.jpg&h=77774bf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普將於下周二（12日），在新加坡與朝鮮領袖金正恩舉行峰會。新加坡官方鑄幣廠今日公布，推出3款「特金會」紀念幣，售價介乎36至1380新加坡元（約211至8118港元）。<br />\n<br />\n紀念幣分別以鋅鍍鎳、1安士999純銀及半安士999.9純金3種，其中一面鑄有在美國及朝鮮國旗前握住的兩隻手、兩國國名、美朝峰會日期及「SUMMIT IN SINGAPORE」字樣，另一面則有美國國花玫瑰和朝鮮國花迎紅杜鵑、象徵和平的白鴿和橄欖枝，及「WORLD PEACE」（世界和平）字樣。<br />\n<br />\n是次美朝峰會將是歷來首次在任美國總統與朝鮮領袖間的會談，美國上月亦曾推出據報是美國軍方鑄造的紀念幣，但其後特朗普突稱要取消峰會，「早產」紀念幣需減價求售，引來大批網民嘲諷。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180605/s00005/1528191490613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180605%2Fs00005%2F1528191490613&d=NsE7wDIgqlO59o5HwdL984zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=81e80524\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180605%2Fs00005%2F1528191490613&h=0b74a09d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180605/s00005/1528191490613</a>"},{"pid":"79d76509d1b67749875b05ea37c660d16a27beb1","tid":691191,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T13:25:13.000Z","msg":"中國最後或成為最大贏家"},{"pid":"5b37d404f758e70759737cefda2e87a48c1f19d6","tid":691191,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T13:26:14.000Z","msg":"香港<img src=\"/asset